des:
EKO Home products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your plug.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your plug - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your EKO Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "EKO Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "EKO Home" app;
(3). You need to have some EKO Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "EKO Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "EKO Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "EKO Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "EKO Home", and you'll be navigated to "EKO Home" login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom plug.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom plug.”
